Possible Human E. Coli Transmission Seen, Hannoversche Says

-- B y   E v a   v o n   S c h a p e r
-- 
2011-06-10T06:53:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-10/possible-human-e-coli-transmission-seen-hannoversche-says.html
Officials in the German state of
Hesse are probing a possible case of human transmission of the
bacterial E.coli infection,  Hannoversche Allgemeine Zeitung 
reported, citing people close to the investigation.  A caterer may have spread the infection to guests at a
party in Goettingen; eight of whom have already fallen ill, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eva von Schaper in Munich at 
 evonschaper@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at 
 pserafino@bloomberg.net  